Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:08.74,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs23}You brat! You've messed with my cute chimeras not once, but twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:11.11,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,"Cute"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:16.04,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs23}What are you all standing around for?!\NHurry and catch that punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:17.35,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:19.08,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:22.35,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,I'll dispose of him myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:29.36,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:30.56,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:32.29,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Oh, I found something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.29,0:00:33.63,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:40.94,Helvetica,,0,0,3,,{\fs23}Hey, brat! What do you think you're doing?!\NThat's my sacred regimental flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.21,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:46.03,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:46.41,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,{\move(256,440,256,429,0,400)}You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:46.44,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,{\move(256,400,256,440,0,2)}You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:46.47,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,{\move(256,400,256,450,0,2)}You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:47.51,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:53.68,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,You punk...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:58.15,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:06.16,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,No chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.16,0:01:08.40,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.40,Helvetica,,0,0,410,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:10.33,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,He’s got some good shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.77,0:01:14.54,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,By the way, brother, where are we heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.54,0:01:17.11,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Hmm? I guess over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.11,0:01:19.84,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:19.84,Helvetica,,0,0,410,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:32.25,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.72,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Oh... is that...
